.row
  .col-md-12.text-center
    h3(translate='') Applications for use img.bi
    hr
.row
  .col-md-4
    h4
      a(href='https://github.com/imgbi/imgbi-client') imgbi-client
      br
      small(translate='') command-line, node.js
    p
      span(translate='') License
      | : 
      a(href='http://opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php') MIT
    code npm install imgbi -g
  .col-md-8
    p(translate='')
      | Just a simple command-line client for uploading/downloading/deleting images. Also can be used in Node.js applications.
    pre.
      \n$ imgbi-client -i image.png
      https://img.bi/#!XqL4IVp!jxJccrgkodebbxlaplteabgtbkllab5tberiWkam
      https://img.bi/rm/#!XqL4IVp!jxJccrgkodebbxlaplteabgtbkllab5tberiWkam!Rl80pmqeXIgRhZz9TQvCrYLAIAi
      $ imgbi-client -d 'https://img.bi/#!XqL4IVp!jxJccrgkodebbxlaplteabgtbkllab5tberiWkam' -o images
      OK: Saved to XqL4IVp.png
      $ imgbi-client -r 'https://img.bi/rm/#!XqL4IVp!jxJccrgkodebbxlaplteabgtbkllab5tberiWkam!Rl80pmqeXIgRhZz9TQvCrYLAIAi'
      OK: Removed      
    p(translate='')
      | More examples in 
      a(href='https://github.com/imgbi/imgbi-client/blob/master/README.md') README
      | .
